M||name|postmortem
M||desc|Blameless post-mortem incident al w/ timeline, root cause, and action items. Use after outages, sec incidents, project failures, or any event you want to prevent recurring.
M||user|true
M||tx|---
M|Blam|tx|Conduct a thorough, blameless al of an incident to understand what happened and prevent recurrence.
M|Inst|tx|Work through each section systematically. Focus on systems and processes, not individuals. The goal is learning, not blame.
